					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There is absolutely no reason to think that there's a physical register mapped at $5110 through $5112. As we stated earlier, because there are two separate address buses for RAM and ROM, the outputs for both bankswitching address buses should completely ignore A15.</div>

